high_descs: Turn left, go half way across the room, turn right, go across the room and turn right toward the desk.
Take the phone from the shelf.
Turn right, go across the room, turn right toward the safe.
Put the phone in the safe.
Go back to the desk.
Pick up the phone from the desk.
Turn around and go back to the safe on the right.
Put the phone in the safe.
anns.task_desc: Put two phones in the safe.

high_descs: Go forward and slightly left, to the space between the desk and file cabinet, then turn right to face the left edge of the desk.
Pick up the white cell phone from shelf above the desk.
Turn right and go past the foot of the bed, then turn right and go to the white safe at the foot of the bed.
Secure the phone in the safe.
Return to the space between the desk and file cabinet and face the desk again.
Grab the cell phone from the desk.
Turn around and carry the phone to the safe at the foot of the bed.
Lock the phone in the safe.
anns.task_desc: Secure two cell phones in a bedroom safe.

high_descs: Turn left, walk to phone on the desk to your right and look up to the shelf.
Grab the phone on the shelf.
Look down, turn right, and walk to the safe by the bed to your right.
Place the phone inside the safe and lock it.
Turn right, walk straight, make a quick right, then turn left to the phone on the desk to your left and look down.
Grab the phone on the desk.
Look up, turn right, then walk to the safe next to the bed to your right.
Place the phone inside standing next to the other phone in the safe and lock the safe.
anns.task_desc: Place two phones inside the safe.
